         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 4516, recto: (1) Horus, son of Harsiesis, son of Horus, has paid to the bank (2) of the northern houses for (3) the silver of poll of year 29, among the men of (4) Pamonthes, son of Paeris, 4 staters. Written in year 29, (5) Epiphi 11.</ab>
